==English==

===Noun===
'''stapler''' (''plural'' '''staplers''')
# A device which binds together sheets of [[paper]] by driving a thin metal [[staple]] through the sheets, folding over the ends of the staple to secure the sheets and avoid injury from the staple’s sharp points.

